{"tid":254400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我都叫左你班把撚唔好做到咁串架啦","createTime":"2017-05-23T07:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T07:59:18.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ec962173406a4dd15a38f6bdd872ca4f65bfa5","tid":254400,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:26:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1477482755899091/?fref=ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1477482755899091%2F%3Ffref%3Dts&d=2JFlxaPkajhGzn5ZGSFtZEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0d6e96a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1477482755899091/?fref=ts</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170523/20170523_f7b06a4c6f3c7390bc7487uXCfXiKUyP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170523%2F20170523_f7b06a4c6f3c7390bc7487uXCfXiKUyP.jpg&h=a78e009e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4903c029525373fb5a0cf8a2d26bd2d1ddb1b57f","tid":254400,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"佢點分人地係咪做UBER"},{"pid":"cc0206ecef9b37120ccc80a058d2b07afea074e0","tid":254400,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:32:16.000Z","msg":"中資「滴滴出行」擬投的士！業界狂呻：投資過億 車行冇得鬥<br />\n<br />\n【新增滴滴出行回應及影片】政府早前建議推出600架專營的士，分3個專營權供業界競投。業界粗略統計，第一筆投資金額至少過億元，一般車行根本無能力承受。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》引消息指，內地「滴滴出行」近日已接觸業界，為競投本港專營的士「摸底」。報道指，「滴滴出行」此舉，一來關心港府推動專營的士是否成功，尤其早前的士業界成立了「撤回的士專營權大聯盟」，曾有的士堵塞立法會及政府總部一帶道路的行動，二來了解香港有哪些公司有興趣競投專營的士，以評估自己的勝算。<br />\n<br />\n「滴滴出行」發言人向本報回應，並無否認向業界「摸底」競投專營的士的傳聞，並指公司扎根本港多年，致力於以技術提升本港的士服務質素及司機收入，對政府政策走向關心是自然的事，希望政策方向日益開明，有助於本港智慧城市發展，也將持續向各界持份者虛心請教與交流。<br />\n<br />\n業界質疑，政府推出專營的士計劃，似為「滴滴出行」此類財雄勢大的企業度身訂做，同時「滴滴出行」旗下「快的Taxi」早已打入香港市場，若它要競爭專營的士權，入場成本已較其他公司低。<br />\n<br />\n滴滴打車於2012年在北京開始出現，於2015年與快的打車合併，並於去年8月收購Uber中國品牌，自此獨霸中國call市場。騰訊（700）、阿里巴巴及Uber亦持有滴滴出行股權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170405/56523383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170405%2F56523383&d=2JFlxaPkajhGzn5ZGSFtZEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=47431198\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170405%2F56523383&h=d55f4a6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170405/56523383</a>"},{"pid":"713d79b832cbcd18108f44686a16b646bb4b09e6","tid":254400,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢點分人地係咪做UBER</blockquote><br />\n<em></em><br />\n真係唔知<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170523/20170523_10503e6f88a6cd5eeccbnHOaqxI1iiIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170523%2F20170523_10503e6f88a6cd5eeccbnHOaqxI1iiIE.jpg&h=bc201d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170523/20170523_93982135ac76cc04cfb7Jv5tfD3jh4PZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170523%2F20170523_93982135ac76cc04cfb7Jv5tfD3jh4PZ.jpg&h=28eeec69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23f57bb6895dcab0956a870bc6fa08f166863087","tid":254400,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:34:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢點分人地係咪做UBER</blockquote><br />\n<em></em><br />\n真係唔知<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170523/20170523_10503e6f88a6cd5eeccbnHOaqxI1iiIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170523%2F20170523_10503e6f88a6cd5eeccbnHOaqxI1iiIE.jpg&h=bc201d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170523/20170523_93982135ac76cc04cfb7Jv5tfD3jh4PZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170523%2F20170523_93982135ac76cc04cfb7Jv5tf