 />\n等睇中資合法競爭</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n政府同中資合作 變左合法 你地班撚屌的士佬聲都出唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047d32cb5fe9bdef0190443b6c8250c68078a117","tid":254400,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢點分人地係咪做UBER</blockquote><br />\n<em></em><br />\n真係唔知<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170523/20170523_10503e6f88a6cd5eeccbnHOaqxI1iiIE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170523%2F20170523_10503e6f88a6cd5eeccbnHOaqxI1iiIE.jpg&h=bc201d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170523/20170523_93982135ac76cc04cfb7Jv5tfD3jh4PZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170523%2F20170523_93982135ac76cc04cfb7Jv5tfD3jh4PZ.jpg&h=28eeec69&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n等睇中資合法競爭</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n政府同中資合作 變左合法 你地班撚屌的士佬聲都出唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多行都係咁<br />\n老屎忽壟斷成行，用各種合法非法手段玩死新競爭者<br />\n跟住中資入侵下收皮"},{"pid":"24b359c2b0e9da0b3718a902793d0b82ff428c2e","tid":254400,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"滴滴入到黎睇你班的士狗仲有咩聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n老屎忽害全行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf38ed1cde5cb440d834badd04285346a54105f","tid":254400,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T07:57:18.000Z","msg":"歷史真係重覆又重覆<br />\n<br />\n中資入主獨霸市場 + 趕走uber <br />\n香港人仲係度犯法就係犯法 企到咁撚高 因住跌死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d435991db99a5fb9c9889988b2cea358d154d7","tid":254400,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"